How To Install SamaCrm

1.Create a mysql database and import database.sql in to your suggested Database

2.Edit /app/config/database.php On line 81 :
  
	'login' => 'user',
	'password' => 'password',
	'database' => 'test_database_name',

3.Go to http://www.google.com/recaptcha and create a recaptcha key and edit /app/config/core.php line 229 and 230 :
Configure::write('Recaptcha.publicKey', 'xxxxxxxx');
Configure::write('Recaptcha.privateKey', 'xxxxx');

4.Visit your home page and login with this information :

Email : you@domain.com
Password : 123456
